# image

## type-a
::: demo
```html
<div class="tui-img-cont type-a">
    <img src="" alt="">
    <span>图片文字</span>
</div>
<style>
.tui-img-cont.type-a {
    width: 300px;
    height: 200px;
    background-color: #eee;
    overflow: hidden;
}
.tui-img-cont.type-a img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.tui-img-cont.type-a span {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background-color: #3ca4e4;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.tui-img-cont.type-a:hover img{
    transform: scale(1.2);
}
.tui-img-cont.type-a:hover span {
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
}
</style>
```
:::

## type-c
::: demo
```html
<div class="tui-img-cont type-c">
    <img src="" alt="">
    <span>图片文字</span>
</div>
<style>
.tui-img-cont.type-c {
    width: 300px;
    height: 200px;
    background-color: #eee;
    overflow: hidden;
}
.tui-img-cont.type-c img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    filter: blur(5px);
}
.tui-img-cont.type-c span {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background-color: rgba(60,164,228,0.2);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #fff;
}
.tui-img-cont.type-c:hover img{
    transform: scale(1.2);
    filter: blur(0px);
}
</style>
```
